lead_paragraph: Holders Barcelona produced a second-half blitz to come from behind and beat Athletic Bilbao 3-1 to book a place in the King's Cup semi-finals after Atletico Madrid crashed out in a shock 3-2 defeat by Celta Vigo.

headline.print_headline: Barca Sink Bilbao as Atletico Crash Out of Cup
